- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is another possible category as the paper deals with network traffic classification. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of DL in image processing and computer vision, which are subfields of CV. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also less likely but possible as DL is a subfield of AI and is used in the paper for traffic classification.
